description:
<!--StartFragment-->

Your love is a very dynamic afrocentric gospel song.

The song talks about the faithful and unwavering love of God . Despite the situations we find ourselves in, or despite who we are, He loves us endlessly.

Produced by the profound producer,**J Beats** this masterpiece serves to deliver that feel good factor while stirring up the spirit of praise in you.
